with obligate symbiotic r e l a t i o n s h i p w i t h m a s s i v e h e x a s t e r o p h o r a n a n d D e m o s p o n g i a e s p o n g e s. P r e s e r v e d p o l y p s 
<quantity box="[163,313,1872,1893]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.7" metricValueMax="3.1" metricValueMin="0.3" pageId="13" pageNumber="336" unit="mm" value="1.7" valueMax="3.1" valueMin="0.3">0.3–3.1 mm</quantity>
in length, 
<quantity box="[461,611,1872,1893]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.1" metricValueMax="3.4" metricValueMin="0.8" pageId="13" pageNumber="336" unit="mm" value="2.1" valueMax="3.4" valueMin="0.8">0.8–3.4 mm</quantity>
